What they mean by so confused a statement, which is ao torn and patched that it contains nothing sound and fresh, you would hardly divine it they had not said in the title oi the work that they dealt with the avoidance of abominable pastors in the church. You must not suppose this is horror of popish pastors. It is against ns they rail in this fashion. For they meet with the popish and do not shun their meetings. We who stand by the gospel are assailed here. The reason is that we alone show up and shun catabaptism and their wholesale sedition.
